        <h2 class="hpt-title">
          Build High-Performing <span class="accent">Remote Teams</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="hpt-intro">
         Whether you're rapidly scaling your operations, searching for niche skills, or striving to optimize costs, we unlock the full potential of a borderless talent pool for you.
        </p>
        <img src={imgSrc} alt={imgAlt} class="hpt-photo w-full h-auto object-cover block lg:hidden" />

        <div class="hpt-body">
